comments.content: You might find something similar at [Fontstruct](http://web.archive.org/web/20080928173448/http:/fontstruct.fontshop.com/). Or, if not, you could build it yourself. :^)
Not sure this is a font - look how different the Q and O are - with the O even a bit asymmetrical.
I’m surprised I didn’t say that it was probably lettered by hand. Agree with Vivicity.
